<li id="text-331622521" class="widget widget_text"><h2 class="widgettitle">Recommended Books</h2>
			<div class="textwidget"><p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0945466056?ie=UTF8&tag=economicsjunkie-20&linkCode=as2&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0945466056">America's Great Depression</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=economicsjunkie-20&l=as2&o=1&a=0945466056" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" />
</p>

<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0865976716?ie=UTF8&tag=economicsjunkie-20&linkCode=as2&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0865976716">The Anti-Capitalistic Mentality</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=economicsjunkie-20&l=as2&o=1&a=0865976716" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" /></p>

<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0452011876?ie=UTF8&tag=economicsjunkie-20&linkCode=as2&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0452011876">Atlas Shrugged</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=economicsjunkie-20&l=as2&o=1&a=0452011876" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" />
</p>

<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0865976643?ie=UTF8&tag=economicsjunkie-20&linkCode=as2&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0865976643">Bureaucracy</a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=economicsjunkie-20&l=as2&o=1&a=0865976643" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important;" /></p>

